    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wars characterized by hit-and-run tactics by small, mobile groups of irregular forces operating in territory controlled by a hostile regular force.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
